<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink389">
<l>ceyviṉaip polinta ceṟikaḻa ṉōṉṟāṇ</l>
<l>maiyaṇaṟ kāḷaiyoṭu paiya viyalip</l>
<l>pāvai yaṉṉaveṉ ṉāytoṭi maṭantai</l>
<l>ceṉṟaṉa ḷeṉṟi raiya</l>
<l>voṉṟiṉa vōvava ḷañcilam paṭiyē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Sir, you said that my doll-like young girl with choice bracelets </l>
<l>has gone, walking softly with her dark-bearded young man </l>
<l>with tight glittering well-crafted anklets on enduring legs.  </l>
<l>Do her feet with pretty anklets touch [the ground]? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
